    <title>Protect Veterans from Financial Fraud Act of 2017</title>
    <createDate>2017-01-04T07:01:11Z</createDate>
    <billNumber>105</billNumber>
    <constitutionalAuthorityStatementText><![CDATA[<pre>[Congressional Record Volume 163, Number 1 (Tuesday, January 3, 2017)]From the Congressional Record Online through the Government Publishing Office [<a href='http://www.gpo.gov'>www.gpo.gov</a>]By Ms. BROWNLEY of California:H.R. 105.Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto the following:Article 1, Section VIII of the U.S. Constitution[Page H49]</pre>]]></constitutionalAuthorityStatementText>
